				<integer>1</integer>
				<key>scriptfile</key>
				<string></string>
				<key>type</key>
				<integer>0</integer>
			</dict>
			<key>type</key>
			<string>alfred.workflow.action.script</string>
			<key>uid</key>
			<string>run-script-01</string>
			<key>version</key>
			<integer>2</integer>
		</dict>
	</array>
	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Type "tsvg" followed by a brand name to search theSVG.

Enter: Copy raw SVG to clipboard
Cmd+Enter: Copy CDN URL to clipboard
Alt+Enter: Copy markdown image syntax to clipboard

The icon registry is cached for 6 hours at ~/Library/Caches/com.glincker.thesvg-alfred/</string>
